{"id": "1500929926704926840", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "author_id": "735137568307282011", "author_name": "reya.li", "content": "When using a Wheel of Destiny or experiencing an effect that increases Xu's aliemus generation by a percentage (in the video's case Incalculable Factor WoD was equipped to Xu), in some cases the doubling the Resonance effect of Xu's next command card after an Exalt is just slightly off what it should be.\n\nXu Strike/Defend with Incalculable Factor stats:\n11 Aliemus\n[Resonance] 17 Aliemus\n\nThe expected effect of using this Strike/Defend with Resonance just after an Exalt would be 11 Aliemus + 34 Aliemus (2 Resonances' worth).\n\nInstead in this case you get 11 Aliemus + 33 Aliemus.\n\nThis is a pretty minor bug but I thought I'd report it anyways since it would be understandable if it wasn't noticed for a long time otherwise. <:Doll_Inferno_ha:1459091434958360760>", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T18:39:40.456000+00:00", "thread_id": "1500929926704926840", "attachments": [{"id": "1500929927606964274", "filename": "Screen_Recording_2026-05-04_192536.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 7383916, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1500929926704926840/1500929927606964274/Screen_Recording_2026-05-04_192536.mp4?ex=69fa396c&is=69f8e7ec&hm=d93d38c1068318a3059f198628d59554ebfd948f687c69c386b4fbc69c51b287&"}, {"id": "1500929928219197600", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1371590, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1500929926704926840/1500929928219197600/image.png?ex=69fa396c&is=69f8e7ec&hm=a483f8efcb4d9fb5d258f9b6d2de64fdfdc51957cd03b118de74a02cd2db515a&"}]}
