{"id": "1500991756257464412", "channel_id": "1500991756257464412", "author_id": "845527584157597716", "author_name": "lurenjiao", "content": "1，商店现在仅可以购买未溢出的命轮。\n      1）首先是这个改动为什么不在前瞻或者 “ 首次 ” 更新公告里面提及？如果提前告知了，玩家可以酌情考虑提前分解一部分命轮进行理财。仅在公告中告知新版本无法分解命轮而不提及商店改动，很难不让人联想动机。当然了，你也可以说这是发公告的疏忽，那既然是疏忽就应该拿出补偿。\n      2）此改动导致老玩家缺少的收益。假设一位已经氪金解锁的3种课题命轮的老玩家：沉淀商店6组命轮各3次，都溢出的情况下是18个精粹灵核碎片和54个灵核碎片，无光商店4组命轮各3次，都溢出的情况下是12个灵核碎片和36个灵核碎片，融珠商店3组命轮各3次，都溢出的情况下是9个精粹灵核碎片和27个灵核碎片。  **合计每个月损失39个精粹原初碎片和117个灵核碎片。**\n      3）4种溢出的材料应该如何使用？调查徽章的溢出问题从1周年之前就在反馈，到目前位置未曾得到回应。现在另外三个有消耗渠道的商店删除了很多道具，那后续溢出材料会一直变多，最终只能变成蔷薇金券，但是有部分玩家已经不缺玫瑰金券了，那溢出资源应该如何处理呢？在删除商店道具前是否想过老玩家的利益。能不能增加商店可以兑换的内容。\n2，溢出转化。\n      1）这个事情对于大多数玩家来说应该是好事，但是如果有缺灵核不缺自选道具的玩家怎么办？为什么不保留可以选择的途径。\n      2）一个月只能换3个自选。假如我灵核转换自选材料的兑换额度是好几百呢，而且现在没有商店溢出兑换以后，灵核产出也减半了，换到关服都换不完了，这怎么办？", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T22:45:21.770000+00:00", "thread_id": "1500991756257464412", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-04T22:47:42.632000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "IMG_20251113_181453", "emoji_id": "1448240235757568133", "count": 11}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "😾", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1500991756894732408", "filename": "827791f8af2d9c5772d5e6bbe1eeae2e.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2391528, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1500991756257464412/1500991756894732408/827791f8af2d9c5772d5e6bbe1eeae2e.png?ex=69fb1bc1&is=69f9ca41&hm=ba6499ea4943858f87005bd377c6780552c32061255144e8b118ec6cef1374cf&"}, {"id": "1500991757544980561", "filename": "f5b8f79016425bc5651ae37979386ae8.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2389760, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1500991756257464412/1500991757544980561/f5b8f79016425bc5651ae37979386ae8.png?ex=69fb1bc2&is=69f9ca42&hm=ba29dc146adc299d266a51f66963fb86170c3ef455a699d576707ab7f3e66161&"}]}
{"id": "1500961894352293978", "channel_id": "1500961894352293978", "author_id": "366684591236448259", "author_name": "justanothergenericusername", "content": "While using Agrippa in D-Zone, I encountered a bug with her Reluctant Alms, where the discounted Colorless Spiral would not retain the decreased Arithmetica cost after returning to hand via triggering Devour. I checked and confirmed this to be the issue, as Agrippa's own Soulforged Aptitude passive was functioning correctly.", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T20:46:42.137000+00:00", "thread_id": "1500961894352293978"}
{"id": "1500949657155801309", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "author_id": "298140360603992066", "author_name": "exo_2360", "content": "Isn't this just a result of rounding during the calculation of incalc's effecf?\n15 * 1.075 = 16.125 (gets rounded up to 17)\n30 * 1.075 = 32.25 (gets rounded up to 33)", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T19:58:04.562000+00:00", "thread_id": "1500929926704926840"}
{"id": "1500968919207510026", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "author_id": "735137568307282011", "author_name": "reya.li", "content": "Probably, it did cross my mind, but it doesn't really matter if so since everything in the game with stat-scaling is supposed to (and usually does) round up after each individual step of a calculation. The final Resonance number should be doubled rather than any undisplayed pre-rounding number.", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T21:14:36.993000+00:00", "type": 19, "thread_id": "1500929926704926840", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-04T21:18:28.402000+00:00", "mentions": ["298140360603992066"], "reply_to": "1500949657155801309"}
{"id": "1501001318498566145", "channel_id": "1500929926704926840", "author_id": "1280181546527096993", "author_name": "fjantsa", "content": "It doubles the resonance effect which is 15, not your aliemus bonus.\nwhether this is intended/expected or not idk but that's what you are getting.", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T23:23:21.586000+00:00", "thread_id": "1500929926704926840", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-04T23:47:06.631000+00:00"}
